(60, 8, 'life and health single only', '1713755403-6625d50b94ea6.png', '<p>asldkfj laksd jfa jsdlf alsdf ja dfasdf asdf</p>\r\n\r\n<p>asldkfj laksd jfa jsdlf alsdf ja dfasdf asdfasldkfj laksd jfa jsdlf alsdf ja dfasdf asdfasldkfj laksd jfa jsdlf alsdf ja dfasdf asdf</p>\r\n\r\n<p>asldkfj laksd jfa jsdlf alsdf ja dfasdf asdfasldkfj laksd jfa jsdlf alsdf ja dfasdf asdfasldkfj laksd jfa jsdlf alsdf ja dfasdf asdf</p>\r\n\r\n<p>asldkfj laksd jfa jsdlf alsdf ja dfasdf asdf</p>\r\n\r\n<p>asldkfj laksd jfa jsdlf alsdf ja dfasdf asdfasldkfj laksd jfa jsdlf alsdf ja dfasdf asdfasldkfj laksd jfa jsdlf alsdf ja dfasdf asdf</p>', 'asd fsa dfas df', NULL, 364, 500, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 100000, 50000, 2000, NULL, NULL, NULL, 50000, 2000, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 10000, NULL, 10000, 10000, 2000, 5, 3, 3, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 50000, 20000, 1200, 500, 500, 500, 500, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 9, '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 17, NULL, 'Instasure', NULL, 266, 10, NULL, 10, NULL, '7', '5', 'CAUSES OF EXCLUSION FOR DEATH CLAIM\r\n\r\na) All pre-existing disease related Death;\r\nb) Death caused by self-inflicted injury or the commission of or attempted commission of an assault or any unlawful act, or being engaged in any illegal activity or felony;\r\nc) By participating in illegal activity is not covered;\r\nd) Suicide while sane or insane;\r\ne) The condition of Acquired Immune Deficiency Syndrome (AIDS), or any AIDS related illness or HIV virus.\r\n\r\n\r\nExclusions for Hospitalization\r\n\r\n1. Hospitalization due to any illness or disability or any condition pre-existing or preceding the effective date of coverage commencement\r\n2. Less than 24 hours of hospitalization;\r\n3. Any maternity treatment related hospitalization;\r\n4. Advice or treatment received from any person other than a MBBS doctor and not registered with Bangladesh Medical & Dental Council (BMDC);\r\n5. Hospitalization due to the condition of Acquired Immune Deficiency Syndrome (AIDS), and HIV (Human Immune Deficiency Virus), or any AIDS related illness or HIV virus\r\n6. Hospitalization due to any Psychiatric, mental or nervous disorder\r\n7. Hospitalization due to exposure of the body, voluntarily or not, to nuclear power or radioactivity in war or warlike operations or in peace\r\n8. Hospitalization for childbirth, prenatal/postnatal care, or any maternity related conditions\r\n9. Any Dental and optical treatments\r\n10. Any congenital infirmity\r\n11. Hospitalization without a recommendation from a registered physician\r\n12. Circumcision, prophylactic, and immunization procedures\r\n13. Mental, emotional, or psychiatric disorders, alcoholism, or any other narcotic addictions\r\n14. Injury arising due to accident while participating in any unlawful activities, attempted suicide, violation or attempted violation of the law, injuries willfully or intentionally self-inflicted or due to insanity or under the influence of a drug;\r\n15. Obesity, i.e., treatment for, or required as a result of obesity, any cosmetic or plastic treatment/surgery, unless needed as reconstructive surgery as a consequence of an injury due to accidents, or burns\r\n16. Any experimental or generally unaccepted procedures by medical professionals, i.e., acupuncture, herbal/ayurvedic/homeopathy treatment, alternative medical care (AMC), etc.\r\n17. Non-surgical treatment for tuberculosis, hepatitis B, hepatitis C and any other vaccinations, all expenses incurred in connection with the donor for any treatment, lupus and other connective tissue and autoimmune disorders and costs of prostheses, corrective devices,\r\n18. Any treatment for Cancer, radiotherapy, chemotherapy, dialysis;\r\n19. Any treatment provided free by the government.\r\n20. Any charges for food or food supplements (Hotlinks, Viva, Bourn vita etc) cosmetic creams or oils of any nature, water purifiers, etc. are excluded.\r\n21. Three months waiting period will be followed in case of hospitalization due to same disease/disability.\r\n\r\nExclusions For Disability Benefit\r\n\r\na. attempted suicide or intentionally self-inflicted injury, while sane or insane,\r\nb. war, invasion, act of foreign enemy, hostilities (where war be declared or not), armed or unarmed truce, civil war, mutiny, rebellion, revolution, insurrection, military or usurped power, riots, strike, civil commotion, assault, terrorist act, homicide or any war like operations,\r\nc. service (including peace time training) in any military, naval, police air force or similar service, in time of declared or undeclared war or while under orders for war like operations or restoration of public order,\r\nd. making an arrest as an officer of the law,\r\ne. committing a felony,\r\nf. failure to seek or follow medical advice,\r\ng. participation by the insured member in a criminal or unlawful act,\r\nh. any injury incurred before the effective date of the cover,\r\ni. engaging in or taking part in professional sport(s) or any hazardous pursuits, including but not limited to, diving or riding or any kind of race, underwater activities involving the use of breathing apparatus or not, martial arts, hunting, manoeuvring, parachuting, bungee-jumping,\r\nj. accident occurring while or because the Insured Member is affected by alcohol or any drugs, narcotics or psychotropic substances,\r\nk. service, travel or flight in or descent from any kind of aircraft, except as a passenger in an aircraft operated by a commercial passenger airline on a scheduled air service over an established passenger route.\r\nl. Nuclear contamination; the radioactive, explosive or hazardous nature of nuclear fuel materials or property contaminated by nuclear fuel materials or accident arising from such nature.', 'CAUSES OF EXCLUSION FOR DEATH CLAIM\r\n\r\na) All pre-existing disease related Death;\r\nb) Death caused by self-inflicted injury or the commission of or attempted commission of an assault or any unlawful act, or being engaged in any illegal activity or felony;\r\nc) By participating in illegal activity is not covered;\r\nd) Suicide while sane or insane;\r\ne) The condition of Acquired Immune Deficiency Syndrome (AIDS), or any AIDS related illness or HIV virus.\r\n\r\n\r\nExclusions for Hospitalization\r\n\r\n1. Hospitalization due to any illness or disability or any condition pre-existing or preceding the effective date of coverage commencement\r\n2. Less than 24 hours of hospitalization;\r\n3. Any maternity treatment related hospitalization;\r\n4. Advice or treatment received from any person other than a MBBS doctor and not registered with Bangladesh Medical & Dental Council (BMDC);\r\n5. Hospitalization due to the condition of Acquired Immune Deficiency Syndrome (AIDS), and HIV (Human Immune Deficiency Virus), or any AIDS related illness or HIV virus\r\n6. Hospitalization due to any Psychiatric, mental or nervous disorder\r\n7. Hospitalization due to exposure of the body, voluntarily or not, to nuclear power or radioactivity in war or warlike operations or in peace\r\n8. Hospitalization for childbirth, prenatal/postnatal care, or any maternity related conditions\r\n9. Any Dental and optical treatments\r\n10. Any congenital infirmity\r\n11. Hospitalization without a recommendation from a registered physician\r\n12. Circumcision, prophylactic, and immunization procedures\r\n13. Mental, emotional, or psychiatric disorders, alcoholism, or any other narcotic addictions\r\n14. Injury arising due to accident while participating in any unlawful activities, attempted suicide, violation or attempted violation of the law, injuries willfully or intentionally self-inflicted or due to insanity or under the influence of a drug;\r\n15. Obesity, i.e., treatment for, or required as a result of obesity, any cosmetic or plastic treatment/surgery, unless needed as reconstructive surgery as a consequence of an injury due to accidents, or burns\r\n16. Any experimental or generally unaccepted procedures by medical professionals, i.e., acupuncture, herbal/ayurvedic/homeopathy treatment, alternative medical care (AMC), etc.\r\n17. Non-surgical treatment for tuberculosis, hepatitis B, hepatitis C and any other vaccinations, all expenses incurred in connection with the donor for any treatment, lupus and other connective tissue and autoimmune disorders and costs of prostheses, corrective devices,\r\n18. Any treatment for Cancer, radiotherapy, chemotherapy, dialysis;\r\n19. Any treatment provided free by the government.\r\n20. Any charges for food or food supplements (Hotlinks, Viva, Bourn vita etc) cosmetic creams or oils of any nature, water purifiers, etc. are excluded.\r\n21. Three months waiting period will be followed in case of hospitalization due to same disease/disability.\r\n\r\nExclusions For Disability Benefit\r\n\r\na. attempted suicide or intentionally self-inflicted injury, while sane or insane,\r\nb. war, invasion, act of foreign enemy, hostilities (where war be declared or not), armed or unarmed truce, civil war, mutiny, rebellion, revolution, insurrection, military or usurped power, riots, strike, civil commotion, assault, terrorist act, homicide or any war like operations,\r\nc. service (including peace time training) in any military, naval, police air force or similar service, in time of declared or undeclared war or while under orders for war like operations or restoration of public order,\r\nd. making an arrest as an officer of the law,\r\ne. committing a felony,\r\nf. failure to seek or follow medical advice,\r\ng. participation by the insured member in a criminal or unlawful act,\r\nh. any injury incurred before the effective date of the cover,\r\ni. engaging in or taking part in professional sport(s) or any hazardous pursuits, including but not limited to, diving or riding or any kind of race, underwater activities involving the use of breathing apparatus or not, martial arts, hunting, manoeuvring, parachuting, bungee-jumping,\r\nj. accident occurring while or because the Insured Member is affected by alcohol or any drugs, narcotics or psychotropic substances,\r\nk. service, travel or flight in or descent from any kind of aircraft, except as a passenger in an aircraft operated by a commercial passenger airline on a scheduled air service over an established passenger route.\r\nl. Nuclear contamination; the radioactive, explosive or hazardous nature of nuclear fuel materials or property contaminated by nuclear fuel materials or accident arising from such nature.', 1, '13', '03', 'B', NULL, 1, NULL, '4', NULL, NULL, 'LifePkg', NULL, 0, 1, NULL, '2024-10-08 07:33:13', '2024-10-27 11:29:26'),
